	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Here I encountered a problem with crystal bonus count at the end of stage. Since they are "unavoidable" on your route it's better to collect 150 of them, which is the amount when the game begins to count them two at a time.
	$LF
	"00FFBF33 is the memory address and it counts a bit strangely, but I'm not bothering to write it here.
	$LF
